window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Tallulah is confident, happy, and looking for love.</b></p> <p>At least, on the outside.</p> <p>Evrin is kind, thoughtful, and has plenty of love to give.</p> <p>At least, on the inside.</p> <p>In a world where it feels like they're the only ones who don't know where they belong, can Tallulah and Evrin find that sense of home in each other?</p> <p>Or will they be too afraid to take a chance?</p> <p>Invidia <i>is the fifth book in the Shades of Sin series, featuring humans and their not-quite-so-human partners. Each book is a standalone, but best enjoyed in order. For mature listeners.</i></p>"; 
